Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.25,0:01:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本以為結束了我都在笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.02,0:01:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙和那個逸扎卻又出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.88,0:01:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊正在為了讓亞加瑪離開殖民衛星而拚命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯繫信號卻很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.07,0:01:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那兩個人接近了亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z的狀況也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果 我還是用了光束步槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九話 宇宙的捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們殖民地香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙中看起來的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是港口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.73,0:02:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個玫瑰小子馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.15,0:02:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想讓安多拉離開香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像那種怪人最讓人頭痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真傷腦筋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲到底在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機還沒到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉比安羅茲的會合?地點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,都怪這裏垃圾太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才也是這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.54,0:03:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,附近沒有動靜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看2加2...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視情況怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,沒有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊也到處是垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們認真點阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.06,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與在香格里拉時的態度\n完全不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,借給我啊\n不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不是運動場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是拿這個給艦長看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太大了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再小一點才能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再繼續尋找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.81,0:03:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.76,0:04:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冠武,那不是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.58,0:04:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要\n還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,幹什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她可能迷路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路她怎麼不講?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她那麼倔強,不會講的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們自己來找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先找到的話\n露卡會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒空去討小孩的歡心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話是這樣說沒錯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇斯洛,用雷達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米諾夫斯基粒子濃度不高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要好好檢定方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓敵人發現我們\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多拉傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不修理密達斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能飛就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花姊姊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這個假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險,退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是假隕石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會太小?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.24,0:05:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.81,0:05:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個放在宇宙中\n還會增加五十倍大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.44,0:05:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼大...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那MS不就可以躲在這個後面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假隕石\n不是只有隕石形狀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模仿殖民地殘骸而做的假鋼板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.29,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來是很小...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數量多的時候\n就可以用來隱藏亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝上炸彈也能成為氣雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比米諾夫斯基粒子更好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS戰時也能應用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那為什麼特雷斯你開密達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時不用假隕石?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有必要光使用武力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為當時是在殖民地內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧,特雷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...對阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請來看房間分配圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分配房間?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼可以擅自決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.27,0:06:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別計較嘛\n又不可能顧到所有人的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.38,0:06:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的房間也得換嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個當然有考慮到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟學校一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟學校一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來,伊諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆,來就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點發出強力電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉就能知道亞加瑪的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出賣亞加瑪太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!你仔細想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再打下去我們又贏不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如把亞加瑪賣給安多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.94,0:06:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們回香格里拉更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.07,0:06:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要背叛亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是不依賴大人才活下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別到宇宙就變了一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.91,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為捷杜會撐很久嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真以為他是新人類嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去香格里拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過過好日子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.02,0:07:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把亞加瑪賣掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.44,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就能買新MS了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再撿破爛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.82,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別妨礙我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.41,0:07:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並不適合再亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.47,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就到MS甲板上面去\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,你再做什麼??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現強力電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.74,0:07:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!幾秒就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是電波強的不尋常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.94,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亞加瑪嗎?確認位置了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是亞加瑪的話\n就不太正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像故意告訴我們位置似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.69,0:08:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材,亞加瑪內有內奸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦...\n我們與香格里拉市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.95,0:08:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和好相處的努力成果出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.56,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪內部有人支持亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯有得到市民的信賴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指揮官才可能有好的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你必須親近市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與他們打成一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是\n這是身為領導者必須注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎?馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.12,0:08:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會盡量注意的,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內奸?真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給內奸看看亞古捷斯的誠意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用哈瑪哈瑪過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人一定會贊成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.84,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人\n請讓我派人支援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看這MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它的魄力與重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達根本不是對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.98,0:09:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有新型MS哈瑪哈瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.38,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才是究極的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有他在,我就必勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.71,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們一生最大的請求\n馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.10,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我們\n幫馬士文大人你的忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.62,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幾個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.13,0:09:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧,隨便你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擁有一群好部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈瑪哈瑪,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.74,0:09:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒到宇宙了\n心情也跟著雀躍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等著吧,亞加瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我終於要開動MS實際作戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.23,0:10:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在東張西望什麼東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沉不住氣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連亞加瑪都跟丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.76,0:10:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭!我叫他們要好好跟著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小孩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抬起頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是哪一個部隊的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說出所屬艦名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.34,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所屬艦名?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這...我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.17,0:11:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是突然被召集的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後就被趕鴨子上架做飛行訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在也不知道\n自己是在哪裏飛行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是奧干的人\n還是聯邦軍的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的少女...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你帶這位少女去安多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑?馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我初次上陣阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們新手駕駛員來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟生日一樣可貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太囉唆了,敢不聽命令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.73,0:11:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼馬士文大人對女人\n都這麼溺愛呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,我會想辦法自己回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.25,0:12:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼客氣話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.48,0:12:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們亞古捷斯\n是各位市民的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.81,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明,別怠慢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不虧是地球圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有讓我ㄧ眼就迷上的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太感謝你了,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禍不單行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,只好順著形勢去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.60,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想跟你說一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現敵人MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是上次的敵人,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不同MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入第一備戰狀態\nZ高達出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解,MS...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放出假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉杜艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫捷度快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用之前用的大炮迎敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螢幕全打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!我要跟你談阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不穿太空衣你會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦橋,知道敵人的數目嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.16,0:13:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他可出動的MS呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你沒立場說那種話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的船員中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最擅長駕駛Z高達的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比花更厲害不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得倒是很簡單阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯蘭治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他Z高達的資料\n馬上送他出陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的,捷度是新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.92,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪被擊沉,你也一樣要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也沒必要要我先死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.51,0:14:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.48,0:14:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你過去對Z高達\n的操作就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別拍馬屁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會上當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你無處可去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.49,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想你住在亞加瑪上面的同伴死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.80,0:14:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妹妹也在阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\n我關艙門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.05,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人有5架,好像更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候該說什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達,Z高達出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度那小子\n忘記來福槍的能源盒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.39,0:15:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,我們去作戰鬥後食物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,冠武,來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才剛做完午餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人沒吃午飯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們可能是空著肚子作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以老是這麼弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擋著,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.07,0:15:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去找各位子坐吧\n是...是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼多資料我看不完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一次看這麼多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼會懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是被敵人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.18,0:16:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,只有一架Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.26,0:16:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙,我只有一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了!明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.41,0:16:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙中我是不會手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有能源了...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘記帶能源盒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來決鬥吧,Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.09,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙中你就無處使力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥不只是用蠻力!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.23,0:16:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了!有假隕石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.25,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用來雷射來福槍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.88,0:16:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想逃走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達沒有雷射來福槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.84,0:17:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各機全力飛行直接把它圍起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥時還這樣鬆懈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的飛機,通訊系統沒有壞阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.61,0:17:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼飛機?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小型飛機很少有這麼\n好的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有機艙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是裝飾品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.41,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,是真的,可以用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.31,0:17:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以開槍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧干陣營有正式採用這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.51,0:17:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在這裏會被捲入戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民地的爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也不任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.38,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要當好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.16,0:17:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,你想回家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.79,0:18:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假隕石不知能不能撐的很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.84,0:18:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算跑到隕石群中\n你也逃不掉的,Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是假隕石,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.31,0:18:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,不要跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些氣球太礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別被假隕石騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直線前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.59,0:18:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看你能一直用假隕石到何時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.85,0:18:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們連真假隕石都分不清嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.09,0:18:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙連基本常識都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一次毀3架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼只有1架?數目不對阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你用假隕石太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你5比1不是更卑鄙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是1比1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒意見了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.32,0:19:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時才公平決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我變的更討厭你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,那是敵人的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是Z高達嗎?\n太好了,我真幸運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你帶我過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薩克C隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那戰機\n根再香格里拉看到的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡\n你為什麼攻擊我又跑回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,古利明,你沒受傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.99,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若是受傷我會很為難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為難?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你對我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.93,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\n我是站在亞加瑪那邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.99,0:20:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,馬世文大人去追截你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.24,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了\n我好像快忘記自己的使命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可原諒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先收拾你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了,力量下降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.71,0:20:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我贏了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我有穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.53,0:21:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想不戰而逃嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便你怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪裏面有我們的同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的卑鄙的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會受到報應的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.16,0:21:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是莫名奇妙,跑來偷襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但什麼是也不做就逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人總是有很多理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來你可以擊沉一架MS的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個人真是的\n我是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且被抓去安多拉當人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道我費了多少苦心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃離那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是迷路而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然,我才沒有那麼笨阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.20,0:21:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.72,0:22:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,敵人說亞加瑪有他們的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.87,0:22:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為那是隨便講講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有必要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真單純
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是你聽錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.44,0:22:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.58,0:22:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們兩位了,去休息吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,是拉比安羅茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.05,0:22:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?靠近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.35,0:22:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它發現到我們了\n是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.37,0:23:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為拉比安玫瑰不能接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.34,0:23:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花拚死出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.58,0:23:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.68,0:23:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪內卻出現了幫助馬士文的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.45,0:23:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是露幹得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.43,0:24:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從拉比安玫瑰運來了新型的戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.33,0:24:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可不能指望偽裝隕石啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.07,0:24:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 再見了，花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.73,0:24:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花小姐真是可憐

